<note n="0278001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0278001">恩＝思【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0278002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0278002">簡＝揀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0279002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0279002">賈＝估【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
